	<content><![CDATA[const digitize = n => [...('' + n)].map(i => parseInt(i));]]></content>
	<description>Converts a number to an array of digits.  Convert the number to a string, using spread operators in ES6(`[...string]`) build an array. Use `Array.map()` and `parseInt()` to transform each value to an integer.</description>
